Frigid_Bolt.help: You fire a bolt of death energy at your target. This causes them to suffer reduced movement and attack speeds, as well as cold and negative energy damage.
Frigid_Bolt.shortHelp: Ranged, Minor DMG (Cold/NegativeEnergy), -DEF(Cold/Negative Energy), -RES(Cold/Negative Energy), -Speed(Foe, All), -Rech(Foe)
Frigid_Bolt.targetHelp: Your defense against and resistance to cold and negative energy attacks has been reduced. Your movement and attack speeds have been reduced.

Reapers_Bolt.help: You unleash a concentrated bolt of death energy at a single target. The affected target suffers from negative energy damage over time, endurance drain and reduced recovery.
Reapers_Bolt.shortHelp: Ranged (Secondary Target), Moderate DMG(Cold), Minor DoT(Negative Energy), EndDrain, -Rec
Reapers_Bolt.targetHelp: Your endurance is being drained and you are suffering from a reduced recovery rate.

Frigid_Blast.help: A slower, more powerful bolt of death energy is unleashed at a single target. This causes cold and negative energy damage, as well as reduced movement and attack speeds. The affected target also suffers from a reduced chance to hit.
Frigid_Blast.targetHelp: Your movement and attack speeds have been reduced. You are also suffering from a reduced chance to hit.

Frigid_Lance.help: You unleash a crystal of pure death energy at a single target. This target suffers significant cold and negative energy damage. Additionally, the target endures endurance drain and reduced regeneration and recovery rates. There is a high chance that the affected target also experience increased endurance cost for their powers.
Frigid_Lance.targetHelp: Your endurance is being drained. Your regeneration and recovery rates have been reduced. Additionally, there is a chance that your endurance costs have been increased.

Consuming_Burst.help: You coalesce an orb of crystalline death energy and throw it at a single target. When the orb hits the target, it explodes in a shower of deadly shrapnel. The main target, and all those caught in the burst radius, suffer cold damage. Additionally, their protections against further cold damage are reduced and their endurance costs are increased.
Consuming_Burst.shortHelp: TAoE (Secondary Target), Moderate DMG (Cold), Minor DoT(Cold), -DEF(Foe,Cold), -RES(Foe,Cold), +EndCost(Foe)
Consuming_Burst.targetHelp: You are freezing, taking cold damage over time. Additionally, your protections against cold damage are reduced and your powers cost more endurance to execute.

Earthshatter.help: You stomp your foot into the ground, unleashing a shock of death energy that shakes the shadow realm. This causes damage to foes all around you. Additionally, the roof begins to cave in, which deals continuous damage to enemies who remain close as they are hit with the shrapnel.
Earthshatter.shortHelp: PBAoE, Moderate DMG (Smashing/Cold/Negative Energy), Minor DoT (Lethal), Knockup(Foe), -Fly(Foe), DoT(Lethal), -RES(Foe, Heal), -Speed(Foe,All)
Earthshatter.targetHelp: You have been caught in Diabolique's Earthshatter and are suffering lethal damage over time, as well as reduced movement speed and healing effectiveness.

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} shakes the shadow realm with her {PowerName}.

Soulshatter.help: You begin to shatter the soul of your target, weakening their very being.
Soulshatter.targetHelp: Your soul is being gradually drained by Soulshatter. Eventually, you will be frozen in place, helpless as the coalescing death energy strikes you for significant damage.

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} strikes at your very being with her {PowerName}.

Grant_Consume.help: You consume a Lifegiving Essence, recovering 10% of your health for each consumed. The Essences consumed are destroyed.

Absorbed_Dominance.help: You have nearly completed your ritual to become Death Incarnate. As such, you receive additional bonuses due to the presence of the captured heroes still under your control.
Absorbed_Dominance.targetHelp: You have nearly completed your ritual to become Death Incarnate. As such, you receive additional bonuses due to the presence of the captured heroes still under your control.
